text: Raisins are dried grapes. They have a lot of sugar. Raisins are made in many parts of the world. Raisins can be eaten raw or as part of a recipe. They are well known for being a high protein snack with 500 milligrams of protein. == Other websites == * Cooking.com: Raisins * Natural Benefits and Curative Properties * The World's Healthiest Foods: Raisins * A close-up photo of a raisin == References == Category:Fruits Category:Vitaceae
